title: Stochastic degradation process
text: Degradation models become essential tool analyzing complex systems. last two decades, several degradation models developed capture degradation dynamics systems facilitate decision-making processes. paper aims provide practical guidance statistical analysis common degradation processes help engineers evaluate products effectively. paper introduces three commonly used degradation models: Wiener process, Gamma process, Inverse Gaussian process. degradation process, paper covers data simulation generation, statistical inference, remaining useful life prognostics. summary, paper provides engineers practical guidance analyze data using common degradation models. hoped paper contribute development accurate reliable degradation models can used improve product evaluation decision-making processes various industries.
